cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.DB, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the management of digital libraries, which falls under the category of cs.DL (Digital Libraries). It also discusses techniques for collaboration and coordinated access to knowledge, which could be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
